    "erz.warn":"<strong>For discussion, not advice.</strong> Every scenario is fictional and simplified to spark conversation. The rule references reflect the Texas framework and may change. Verify the current text. Nothing here is legal advice, and the goal is not a single right answer. It is a shared standard of practice you can carry back to your office.",
